l!"],[6969,7182,"What girl wouldn't care about her reputation?"],[7182,7269,"That's vicious."],[7290,7449,"She needs to be thrown out."],[7474,7870,"Toss her out! Toss her out..."],[7870,8229,"Kick her out! Kick her out..."]],"44":[[0,396,"Toss her out! Toss her out..."],[396,492,"Enough!"],[521,625,"This is what you call"],[625,818,"your so-called high society?"],[829,984,"Jumping to conclusions and"],[984,1230,"switching sides, it's disgusting."],[1251,1401,"Enough, Rachel."],[1422,1486,"You're the one"],[1486,1659,"who has to learn some shame."],[1772,2064,"You're the one that says I need shame?"],[2248,2364,"When Sophie was"],[2364,2498,"having her heart attack,"],[2498,2619,"I begged you and"],[2619,2819,"you crushed her lifesaving medication."],[3015,3128,"You made me kneel"],[3128,3259,"and stripped to save her."],[3290,3490,"Is that true? Forcing a mother like that?"],[3541,3657,"They deserve what they got."],[3678,3745,"Enough!"],[3891,3970,"Mommy!"],[4250,4474,"You are a curse."],[4483,4667,"Why couldn't you just stay a nobody, huh?"],[4683,4821,"Why did you have to ruin my life?"],[4833,5025,"Because of you, I lost everything,"],[5059,5221,"my reputation, my career."],[5338,5438,"What are you doing?"],[5472,5793,"I gave you a chance, and now, you die."],[5951,6047,"Mommy!"],[6406,6535,"Don't do this!"]],"45":[[212,271,"Rachel."],[704,796,"Mr. Julian,"],[796,1038,"this is made for Miss Harrington."],[1080,1172,"Are you alright?"],[1447,1530,"Mr. William,"],[1530,1760,"this is made specially for your..."],[2097,2156,"Like it?"],[2540,2681,"Mr. William,"],[2719,2901,"she's just some lowlife orphan."],[2901,3069,"She wouldn't known jewelry from junk."],[3470,3578,"Not your style?"],[3766,4012,"Don't worry, we'll go by the auction and"],[4012,4220,"pick up something way better."],[4629,4783,"Mr. William,"],[4783,4965,"that was a gift for your daughter."],[4965,5096,"Isn't that a bit rude?"],[5113,5296,"You can't treat people like crap"],[5296,5459,"just because you're rich."],[5555,5730,"Wasn't it for my daughter?"],[5776,5951,"I was just checking to see"],[5951,6114,"if my daughter liked it."],[6143,6418,"Mr. William, surely you're joking."],[6431,6543,"Your daughter's not even here."],[6543,6715,"I mean, you were just asking her..."],[6931,6994,"She is..."],[7190,7490,"Allow me to present my daughter"],[7490,7834,"that just returned, Rachel Harrington."]],"46":[[0,166,"No way!"],[166,458,"Rachel can't be the Harrington heiress!"],[746,1013,"You said she was a slum rat!"],[1197,1640,"You single-handedly destroyed the Rhodes!"],[1672,1856,"No, no..."],[1876,2052,"She can't be the heiress."],[2052,2160,"She's just an orphan."],[2160,2331,"Rachel, tell them it's not true."],[2385,2489,"What now?"],[2489,2811,"The power and status you obsessed over"],[2811,2948,"was right there,"],[2998,3190,"but you blew it for good."],[3286,3623,"No, no... this is impossible."],[3728,3929,"You had the nerve to mess with"],[3929,4058,"the Harrington heir!"],[4149,4329,"Clearly, this is just a..."],[4354,4483,"it's a huge misunderstanding."],[4483,4627,"We never would've laid a hand on her"],[4627,4771,"if we knew she was your daughter."],[4800,5142,"Yeah, yeah, it's all Ethan's fault."],[5155,5296,"This was all Ethan's doing."],[5301,5472,"I'll make him apologize."],[6302,6606,"Sir, please, it was... it was just a mistake."],[6619,6744,"Please let us go."],[7119,7399,"Sophie, I'm your dad."],[7440,7657,"Can you... please forgive me?"],[7699,7924,"Can you put in a good word with Grandpa?"],[8249,8387,"Sophie, I haven't gotten to spend"],[8387,8470,"much time with you."],[8470,8742,"Could I have a hug, please?"]],"47":[[1000,1167,"You're not my daddy!"],[1180,1338,"No, Sophie, Sophie!"],[1384,1463,"I am your dad."],[1760,1872,"What kind of man are you,"],[1931,2093,"trying to use your own daughter?"],[2277,2523,"Sophie's your daughter, Ethan."],[2523,2786,"But you never owned up to her!"],[2819,2998,"No need to start now!"],[3023,3169,"You called her a bastard,"],[3240,3378,"even tried to kill her."],[3395,3536,"You're a monster."],[3574,3691,"I am a monster."],[4099,4187,"I let you down,"],[4291,4391,"I let Sophie down."],[4733,4813,"Dad..."],[4959,5034,"I'm tired."],[5100,5184,"Let's go home."],[6239,6489,"Rachel! Sophie! No, no..."],[6489,6606,"Please, please don't go!"],[6648,6752,"Got what he deserved,"],[6752,6898,"ditching someone as gorgeous and rich"],[6898,6965,"as Miss Harrington."],[6977,7148,"Sophie! Rachel!"],[7173,7319,"That's what happens when you're not"],[7319,7444,"cut out for the big leagues."],[7486,7540,"Damn!"],[8258,8491,"Ugh, it's all Rachel's fault."],[8512,8760,"She made my dad look like a drooling idiot."],[9522,9730,"William, president of Harrington Group,"],[9730,9868,"has announced that the return of his"],[9868,10085,"long-lost daughter, Rachel Harrington,"],[10101,10195,"will become the heir to"],[10195,10319,"the Harrington empire."],[10518,10685,"Rachel, I swear you'll pay for this!"]],"48":[[12,125,"Okay, Sophie, sweetheart,"],[125,210,"I'm going to pick you up"],[210,325,"right after my meeting, okay?"],[325,422,"Mm-hmm."],[1626,1714,"Hey, Sophie."],[1985,2097,"Daddy got you a doll."],[2752,2923,"Why bother talking to the kid?"],[2923,3044,"It's Rachel who's gonna pay."],[3207,3340,"Look at that, that's what she wants."],[3340,3406,"Alright."],[3461,3553,"Hello?"],[3687,3837,"Rachel, I have Sophie."],[3849,3999,"You want her back? 10 million."],[4066,4187,"What have you done to her?"],[4212,4320,"No, no, Sophie!"],[4408,4475,"What's wrong?"],[4567,4633,"He..."],[4633,4738,"Ethan has Sophie."],[4767,4879,"Stay calm, alright?"],[4879,4992,"I'm calling in a team now."],[5284,5351,"Mommy!"],[5497,5684,"Madeline, Ethan, let her go."],[5684,5758,"You never told me"],[5758,5880,"you were the Harrington heiress."],[5885,5997,"I never would have left you."],[6001,6210,"Ethan, you did this to yourself."],[6210,6352,"Your greed got you here."],[6368,6539,"Shut up! You ruined me."],[6577,6694,"I'm the real victim here."]],"49":[[16,166,"Let Sophie go!"],[166,262,"Here."],[375,471,"Here's your money!"],[471,558,"Just let Sophie go,"],[558,704,"I'll give you anything!"],[871,921,"Deal."],[1576,1714,"Sophie!"],[2719,3044,"No, no... Let me go, no!"],[3178,3328,"It's over. You're safe."],[3524,3674,"Harrington Group President,"],[3674,3823,"Rachel Harrington, unveils"],[3823,3991,"a global expansion plan."],[4008,4237,"Mommy, you're a rock star!"],[4266,4418,"I want to be just like you!"],[4441,4517,"And you will."],[4517,4700,"You can become whatever you want."],[4750,4879,"Mommy, you haven't"],[4879,5130,"played with me in forever!"],[5171,5242,"Let's go!"],[5296,5363,"Okay."],[5651,5755,"Julian?"],[6715,6944,"Rachel, will you marry me?"]],"50":[[792,1021,"Rachel, will you marry me?"],[1172,1305,"This is unexpected."],[1363,1472,"You've been swamped"],[1472,1609,"running the Group all year."],[1735,1851,"If I didn't pop the question,"],[1851,1972,"William would give me an earful."],[2202,2302,"Julian,"],[2323,2565,"this is your proposal to my daughter."],[2602,2907,"Not a chance to throw me under the bus."],[3620,3883,"Yes, yes, I will."],[4942,5113,"Oh yeah, get in here."]]}